		<title>LASCOFED President At The Cooperative Leaders’ Retreat</title>
		<link>http://lascofed.coop/address-delivered-by-the-lascofed-president-high-chief-oriyomi-ayeola-at-the-cooperative-leaders-retreat-organized-by-ikeja-lagos-island-multipurpose-cooperative-unions-held-16th/</link>
